          "type": "text",
          "name": "t:names.heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Welcome</p><h2>Where Nature Meets Intention</h2><p>Thoughtfully crafted bouquets, grounded in seasonality and designed to make everyday moments feel a little more special.</p><p><a href=\"/collections/all\">Shop all bouquets</a></p>",
