        "text_Kch6J8": {
          "type": "text",
          "name": "t:names.text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>At <strong>Fern & Fauna</strong>, we believe flowers are more than arrangements. They are gestures of celebration, comfort, tenderness, and connection. Our boutique was created to bring thoughtfully crafted bouquets to your doorstep with freshness, elegance, and care.</p><p>We specialize in floral designs that feel personal and quietly refined. Every stem is chosen with intention, every palette is considered, and every bouquet is wrapped to feel meaningful from the moment it arrives.</p>",
