        "text_hWaxUW": {
          "type": "text",
          "name": "t:names.text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Fern & Fauna began with a simple love for the quiet beauty of nature — the way fresh blooms can brighten a room, soften a space, and say what words sometimes cannot. What started as a small idea to share thoughtfully arranged flowers with friends and family soon grew into an online boutique dedicated to crafting meaningful bouquets for every occasion. We wanted to create a store where ordering flowers feels personal, effortless, and special.</p><p>The name Fern & Fauna reflects our philosophy: a balance between lush greenery and delicate blossoms, structure and softness, simplicity and elegance. Each bouquet is carefully curated to feel natural yet refined, combining premium blooms with modern design. We believe flowers should feel intentional — not just beautiful, but meaningful.</p><p>Today, Fern & Fauna continues to focus on quality, freshness, and heartfelt presentation. Every order is handcrafted with care and wrapped to feel like a gift, whether it’s for a celebration, a comfort gesture, or a spontaneous surprise. For us, it’s never just about selling bouquets — it’s about helping people share moments through flowers.</p>",
            "width": "100%",
            "max_width": "none",
            "alignment": "left",
            "type_preset": "rte",
            "font": "var(--font-body--family)",
